casebody.data:
Quordalis V. SANDERS, petitioner,
v.
Carlo ESQUEDA, Dane County Clerk of Court. No. 18-6191. Supreme Court of the United States Dec. 3, 2018.

Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied, and petition for writ of certiorari to the Court of Appeals of Wisconsin, District IV dismissed. See Rule 39.8.
